synopsis: A rookie cop inadvertently captures the murder of a young drug dealer on her body cam. After realizing that the murder was committed by corrupt cops, she teams up with the one person from her community who is willing to help her as she tries to escape both the criminals out for revenge and the police who are desperate to destroy the incriminating footage.
tagline: The truth made her a target.

synopsis: A con man arrives in Mumbai and becomes a mafia don.
Madhurima, a rich girl, falls in love with Raj when they get stranded on an island. But Raj is uninterested, as he is on a mission to avenge his father's death.
A young boy finds himself pursued by two assassins in the Montana wilderness, with a survival expert determined to protect him, and a forest fire threatening to consume them all.
